{% endblock %}

{% block projectTitle %}
    Space Invaders
{% endblock %}

{% block projectType %}
    Personal Project
{% endblock %}

{% block projectDate %}
    November - present
{% endblock %}

{% block projectSummary %}
    A vanilla JS implementation of the classic arcade game, Space Invaders.
    Allows the users to replace the default images with customer ones, like,
    I don't know, photos of politicians that you're not a huge fan of.

{% endblock %}

